WEBVTT

00:01.462 --> 00:02.623
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:02.623 --> 00:04.085
DANIEL DIDN'T DIE
TRYING TO KILL EMILY.

00:04.085 --> 00:05.086
HE SAVED HER.

00:05.086 --> 00:06.887
I HAVE TO START
AT THE BEGINNING

00:06.887 --> 00:09.510
WITH A DAMAGED LITTLE GIRL
NAMED AMANDA CLARKE,

00:09.510 --> 00:11.722
ALSO KNOWN AS EMILY THORNE.

00:11.722 --> 00:14.475
XANAX. CALMS MY NERVES.
[ CHUCKLES ]

00:14.475 --> 00:16.847
THOSE PILLS YOU'RE TAKING --
IT'S COMPOUNDED WITH LARIUM.

00:16.847 --> 00:18.018
YOUR FAMILY'S
BEEN DRUGGING YOU.

00:18.018 --> 00:20.191
AS LONG
AS I'M INCAPACITATED,

00:20.191 --> 00:22.063
MOTHER CONTROLS
THE INHERITANCE.

00:22.063 --> 00:24.105
Victoria:
AS LONG AS MALCOLM BLACK IS OUT
THERE, OUR LIVES ARE IN DANGER.

00:24.105 --> 00:25.276
David:
I'M DEALING WITH HIM.

00:25.276 --> 00:26.817
THREATENING HIM
WITH EVIDENCE

00:26.817 --> 00:28.529
IS A TEMPORARY
SOLUTION AT BEST, DAVID.

00:28.529 --> 00:30.201
GO TO THE FBI
AND ASK FOR PROTECTION.

00:30.201 --> 00:31.652
THEY CAN'T HELP US.
LOOK, I KNOW HOW TO STOP HIM.

00:31.652 --> 00:32.913
THIS HAS TO END.

00:32.913 --> 00:34.415
I WANT YOU TO KNOW, IN CASE
ANYTHING HAPPENS TO ME,

00:34.415 --> 00:35.826
THERE'S A FLASH DRIVE --

00:35.826 --> 00:37.868
EVIDENCE THAT I'VE ACCUMULATED
OF ALL HIS CRIMINAL ACTIVITY.

00:37.868 --> 00:40.461
I-I TURNED IN THE FLASH DRIVE,
ANONYMOUSLY.

00:40.461 --> 00:42.623
THERE WAS ENOUGH EVIDENCE
ON THERE TO PUT HIM AWAY
FOR THE REST OF HIS LIFE.

00:42.623 --> 00:44.925
IF YOU ONLY KNEW
HOW WRONG YOU ARE.

00:44.925 --> 00:46.927
I HEARD A S.W.A.T. TEAM
ARRESTED A GUY NAMED
MALCOLM BLACK EARLIER.

00:46.927 --> 00:48.509
THEY TURNED HIM
OVER TO THE FEDS.

00:48.509 --> 00:49.840
BUT THEN I HEARD
HE WAS RELEASED.

00:49.840 --> 00:52.133
[ WHOOSHING ]

00:52.133 --> 00:53.804
Malcolm:
I CAME FOR YOUR FATHER.

00:53.804 --> 00:54.765
LOOK WHAT I FOUND.

00:54.765 --> 00:56.097
SHH.

00:56.097 --> 00:58.058
NIGHT-NIGHT.

01:09.360 --> 01:11.362
[ GROANING ]

01:13.364 --> 01:15.366
[ GRUNTS ]

01:17.658 --> 01:18.959
OH.

01:18.959 --> 01:20.371
WHAT DID YOU DO?

01:20.371 --> 01:22.373
I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.

01:24.835 --> 01:26.837
THEN WHERE ARE WE?

01:26.837 --> 01:28.839
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

01:33.134 --> 01:36.557
LOOKS LIKE SOME KIND
OF REFUSE DEPOT BY THE WATER.

01:36.557 --> 01:39.270
THE LAST THING I REMEMBER

01:39.270 --> 01:41.021
IS MALCOLM BLACK
AT THE LIGHTHOUSE.

01:41.021 --> 01:42.603
THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.
MALCOLM IS DEAD.

01:42.603 --> 01:45.025
WHAT GAME ARE YOU PLAYING,
EMILY?

01:45.025 --> 01:48.028
Malcolm:
IT'S NOT A GAME, VICTORIA.

01:48.028 --> 01:52.493
AND AS YOU CAN SEE,
I'M VERY MUCH ALIVE.

02:01.202 --> 02:05.666
AND SO IT SEEMS, ARE YOU,
AMANDA CLARKE.

02:05.666 --> 02:07.628
MUST HAVE BEEN REALLY TOUGH,

02:07.628 --> 02:10.800
KEEPING YOUR IDENTITY A SECRET
FOR SO LONG.

02:10.800 --> 02:13.844
WELL, YOUR SECRET'S OUT.

02:17.097 --> 02:19.059
WHAT DO YOU WANT WITH US?

02:19.059 --> 02:21.021
IF IT'S MONEY,
WE'LL PAY IT.

02:21.021 --> 02:24.265
I DON'T NEED YOUR MONEY.

02:24.265 --> 02:25.976
BUT I NEED YOUR HELP.

02:27.107 --> 02:31.942
WE HAVE TO SEND DAVID CLARKE
A WEE MESSAGE.

02:36.237 --> 02:38.078
[ GROANS ]
 [ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

02:41.282 --> 02:43.284
[ PANTING ]

02:47.338 --> 02:49.290
DAVID.

02:49.290 --> 02:50.631
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

02:50.631 --> 02:53.214
I'M SORRY TO BURST
IN HERE LIKE THIS BUT --

02:53.214 --> 02:55.135
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

02:55.135 --> 02:57.718
MALCOLM WON'T BE IN JAIL
FOR LONG.

02:57.718 --> 03:00.100
IT'S BEST IF AMANDA AND I
DISAPPEAR

03:00.100 --> 03:01.892
WHILE WE STILL HAVE THE TIME.

03:01.892 --> 03:04.565
THE FEDS
ALREADY RELEASED HIM.

03:08.188 --> 03:09.650
I TOLD YOU SO.

03:09.650 --> 03:11.442
HE HAS OTHER AGENTS
ON HIS PAYROLL.

03:11.442 --> 03:12.983
WHAT ABOUT
MY FLASH DRIVE?

03:12.983 --> 03:15.866
IT'S ALSO GONE.
 WHEN?

03:15.866 --> 03:17.698
I DIDN'T CALL IN CASE
THEY HAD YOUR PHONE TAPPED.

03:17.698 --> 03:21.372
I WARNED YOU ABOUT THIS,
BUT YOU WOULDN'T LISTEN.

03:24.034 --> 03:26.497
MALCOLM BLACK
WILL BE OUT FOR BLOOD.

03:26.497 --> 03:28.289
THINKS
I DOUBLE-CROSSED HIM.

03:28.289 --> 03:30.711
I DID WHAT I THOUGHT WAS RIGHT.
 YEAH, AND LOOK WHERE
THAT GOT US.

03:30.711 --> 03:32.042
WE HAVE TO ACT FAST.

03:32.042 --> 03:33.334
I'M GONNA GO GET AMANDA.

03:33.334 --> 03:34.505
SHOULD HAVE NEVER --

03:34.505 --> 03:37.097
SHOULDN'T HAVE KEPT HER
IN THE DARK ABOUT THIS.

03:37.097 --> 03:38.549
SHE'S TRAINED FOR IT.

03:38.549 --> 03:40.220
SHE CAN BE AN ASSET.

03:40.220 --> 03:41.892
I'LL LOOK FOR MALCOLM.

03:41.892 --> 03:44.054
WHEN YOU TALKED TO HIM,
DID YOU GET ANY SENSE
OF WHERE HE MIGHT BE,

03:44.054 --> 03:45.396
ANYTHING THAT COULD LEAD ME
TO HIM?

03:45.396 --> 03:46.897
NO, HE'S TOO SMART
FOR THAT,

03:46.897 --> 03:48.899
BUT YOU WERE RIGHT
NOT TO CALL MY CELLPHONE.

03:48.899 --> 03:50.481
HE'S ALREADY TRACKING
MY EVERY MOVE.

03:50.481 --> 03:52.653
HE -- HE'S NOT FAR.

03:52.653 --> 03:56.116
HE THINKS KATE'S
STILL ALIVE, SO HE WON'T
LEAVE HERE WITHOUT HER.

03:56.116 --> 03:59.490
MEET BACK AT GRAYSON MANOR.
WATCH YOUR BACK.

04:04.164 --> 04:06.537
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

04:09.330 --> 04:10.631
I'M STARTING TO THINK

04:10.631 --> 04:12.082
YOU DON'T KNOW THE MEANING
OF "PERSONAL DAYS."

04:12.082 --> 04:14.675
I NEED TO TALK
TO YOU NOW.
 WELL, TAKE IT EASY.

04:17.216 --> 04:19.219
WHAT'S YOUR PROBLEM,
PORTER?
 [ SIGHS ]

04:19.219 --> 04:21.721
I NEED YOU
TO HELP ME FIND SOMEONE --

04:21.721 --> 04:23.013
NO QUESTIONS ASKED.

04:23.013 --> 04:24.385
ALL RIGHT, I'LL BITE.

04:24.385 --> 04:25.976
MALCOLM BLACK.

04:25.976 --> 04:27.688
THE GUY WE JUST TURNED OVER
TO THE FEDS?

04:27.688 --> 04:29.350
THE GUY
THE FEDS JUST RELEASED.

04:29.350 --> 04:31.191
THERE'S A LOT MORE
YOU DON'T KNOW.

04:31.191 --> 04:32.943
LIKE HE WANTS
DAVID CLARKE DEAD?

04:34.315 --> 04:35.486
HOW DID YOU --

04:35.486 --> 04:37.067
THE DAVID CLARKE
WHO WASN'T REALLY IMPRISONED

04:37.067 --> 04:38.198
FOR THE LAST 10 YEARS?

04:38.198 --> 04:40.781
THE FATHER
OF AMANDA CLARKE,

04:40.781 --> 04:42.863
WHO, AS IT TURNS OUT,
IS EMILY THORNE?

04:44.204 --> 04:46.206
I KNOW THE WHOLE STORY,
PORTER.

04:46.206 --> 04:48.409
BEN,
YOU CAN'T TELL ANYONE.

04:48.409 --> 04:49.790
THERE ARE LIVES
AT STAKE HERE.

04:49.790 --> 04:51.622
WELL, I HAVEN'T DECIDED
WHAT I'M GONNA DO YET,

04:51.622 --> 04:53.374
AND AS FOR NEEDING HELP,

04:53.374 --> 04:54.915
I DON'T THINK I'M GONNA PUT
MY LIFE ON THE LINE

04:54.915 --> 04:56.176
FOR A BUNCH OF PEOPLE
WHO'VE BEEN LYING TO ME.

04:56.176 --> 04:58.128
ALL RIGHT, LOOK, YOU HAVE
EVERY RIGHT TO BE PISSED,

04:58.128 --> 04:59.630
BUT THERE'S MORE.

04:59.630 --> 05:01.762
I THINK
THAT ALVAREZ'S DISAPPEARANCE

05:01.762 --> 05:03.053
IS TIED TO MALCOLM, TOO.

05:03.053 --> 05:05.095
SO, YOU THINK HE'S DEAD.

05:05.095 --> 05:08.228
I DON'T KNOW, BUT IF
THERE'S A CHANCE HE'S NOT...

05:11.021 --> 05:13.774
ALVAREZ
SAVED MY ASS YEARS AGO.

05:13.774 --> 05:15.315
I OWE HIM.

05:15.315 --> 05:17.107
MALCOLM HAD DOUBLE AGENTS
WORKING WITH THE FEDS.

05:17.107 --> 05:18.068
HE MIGHT EVEN HAVE PEOPLE

05:18.068 --> 05:19.530
RIGHT HERE
IN OUR OWN DEPARTMENT.

05:19.530 --> 05:21.111
[ SIGHS ]

05:21.111 --> 05:24.995
PLEASE, MAN,
I NEED YOUR HELP.

05:29.790 --> 05:31.582
EMILY?

05:49.810 --> 05:51.231
EMILY!

05:52.473 --> 05:54.855
EMILY?

06:02.483 --> 06:05.325
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

06:11.452 --> 06:14.995
DIDN'T EXPECT TO HEAR
FROM ME AGAIN SO SOON, NOW,

06:14.995 --> 06:16.957
DID YOU, CLARKE?

06:16.957 --> 06:18.999
I TOLD YOU.

06:18.999 --> 06:21.211
YOU'RE OUT OF YOUR LEAGUE.

06:21.211 --> 06:24.715
SO, NOW WE DO THINGS MY WAY.

06:24.715 --> 06:27.558
I WANT MY DAUGHTER BACK,

06:27.558 --> 06:31.221
ALIVE AND UNHARMED.

06:31.221 --> 06:34.184
I'LL GIVE YOU
UNTIL NOON TOMORROW

06:34.184 --> 06:37.568
BECAUSE I WANT
THESE LADIES HERE

06:37.568 --> 06:39.980
TO ENJOY

06:39.980 --> 06:44.114
WHAT MIGHT BE
THEIR LAST NIGHT ON EARTH.

06:44.114 --> 06:46.827
[ VICTORIA BREATHING HEAVILY ]

06:46.827 --> 06:48.619
BRING MY DAUGHTER.

07:06.046 --> 07:09.049
[ DISTORTED VOICES ]

07:14.054 --> 07:16.106
I GOT YOUR MESSAGE.

07:16.106 --> 07:17.147
NO LEADS ON MALCOLM,

07:17.147 --> 07:19.439
BUT I GOT HERE
AS SOON AS I COULD.

07:21.111 --> 07:23.113
IT'S OKAY.

07:23.113 --> 07:25.025
HE KNOWS THE TRUTH
ABOUT EVERYTHING...

07:25.025 --> 07:26.657
INCLUDING EMILY.

07:26.657 --> 07:28.659
SEEMS TO ME YOU CAN USE
ALL THE HELP YOU CAN GET.

07:28.659 --> 07:30.621
HE KIDNAPPED THEM.

07:30.621 --> 07:32.282
HE'S HOLDING THEM
IN EXCHANGE

07:32.282 --> 07:34.074
FOR THE SAFE RETURN
OF HIS DAUGHTER.

07:34.074 --> 07:35.666
WE HAVE TILL NOON.

07:35.666 --> 07:38.078
YEAH,
IF WE COULD GIVE HIM PROOF

07:38.078 --> 07:41.041
THAT KATE WAS STILL ALIVE,
THEN...

07:41.041 --> 07:43.844
YOU KNOW, MAYBE WE
CAN BUY OURSELVES SOME
TIME TO LOOK FOR THEM.

07:43.844 --> 07:45.175
HOW EXACTLY DO YOU PLAN
TO DO THAT

07:45.175 --> 07:47.047
FOR SOMEONE WHO DIED
SEVERAL DAYS AGO?

07:47.047 --> 07:49.720
BY RE-EDITING KATE'S VOICE MEMOS
FROM HER PHONE.

07:49.720 --> 07:51.512
THERE'S NOT ENOUGH TO GO
ON THERE TO FOOL MALCOLM.

07:51.512 --> 07:53.263
JUST BITS AND PIECES --
IT DOESN'T ADD UP TO ANYTHING.

07:53.263 --> 07:55.095
WHAT ABOUT
YOUR BUDDY NOLAN ROSS?

07:55.095 --> 07:56.897
ISN'T HE SOME KIND
OF COMPUTER GENIUS?

07:56.897 --> 07:58.268
I CAN'T PUT
ANYBODY ELSE'S LIFE AT RISK.

07:58.268 --> 07:59.770
SO THAT'S IT?

07:59.770 --> 08:01.361
THERE'S
NO OTHER OPTIONS?

08:01.361 --> 08:03.363
THERE MIGHT BE. THAT'S WHY
I CALLED YOU DOWN HERE.

08:03.363 --> 08:04.985
I WAS HOPING
THAT THIS ISN'T THE ONLY PHONE

08:04.985 --> 08:06.366
THAT I CAN PULL
HER VOICE FROM.

08:22.082 --> 08:25.045
I WAS SO BLIND.

08:25.045 --> 08:29.299
EMILY WENT TO EXTREME MEASURES
TO ENSURE WE ALL WERE.

08:29.299 --> 08:32.092
WHAT ARE WE GOING TO DO
ABOUT IT?

08:32.092 --> 08:35.395
MARGAUX,
THERE'S NOTHING TO DO.

08:35.395 --> 08:39.188
MY FATHER'S DEATH,
YOUR SON'S --

08:39.188 --> 08:41.270
EMILY WAS BEHIND
ALL OF IT.

08:41.270 --> 08:42.482
SHE'S A CRIMINAL.

08:42.482 --> 08:44.144
WHY WOULD YOU NOT WANT
TO PUNISH HER?

08:44.144 --> 08:45.736
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

08:45.736 --> 08:47.738
20 YEARS AGO,

08:47.738 --> 08:49.319
WHEN DANIEL'S LIFE
WAS THREATENED,

08:49.319 --> 08:52.112
I CHOSE TO SAVE HIM,
AND IN SO DOING,

08:52.112 --> 08:54.494
I HURT HER FATHER.

08:54.494 --> 08:56.707
I FEEL I OWE IT TO DAVID.

08:56.707 --> 08:59.289
PLEASE, MARGAUX.

08:59.289 --> 09:02.292
KEEP THIS BETWEEN US.

09:18.558 --> 09:20.520
IT'S MARGAUX LeMARCHAL.

09:20.520 --> 09:22.312
MEET ME TONIGHT.

09:22.312 --> 09:24.645
I NEED YOUR SERVICES.

09:24.645 --> 09:26.647
[ BREATHING HEAVILY,
GRUNTING ]

09:28.609 --> 09:30.611
Malcolm: HEY!

09:30.611 --> 09:33.824
WHY DON'T YOU SAVE YOUR ENERGY?

09:33.824 --> 09:36.787
THERE'S NO WAY
OF GETTING OUT OF THERE.

09:36.787 --> 09:39.960
BUT I DO LOVE
WATCHING YOU TRY.

09:39.960 --> 09:42.082
CHEEKY MONKEYS.

09:44.204 --> 09:46.797
BY MY ESTIMATE,
MALCOLM OR ONE OF HIS MEN

09:46.797 --> 09:48.548
COME BACK TO CHECK ON US
EVERY 30 MINUTES.

09:48.548 --> 09:51.171
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO WORK FAST --
MAYBE MOVE ONE OF THESE BOXES

09:51.171 --> 09:55.175
TO RAM THE GATE
BEFORE HE COMES BACK.

09:55.175 --> 09:56.767
DO YOU HEAR ME?

09:56.767 --> 09:58.769
WE NEED TO MOVE FAST.

09:58.769 --> 10:00.560
WE DON'T HAVE TO DO
ANYTHING.

10:00.560 --> 10:03.894
I'M LOATH TO FOLLOW ANY PLAN
YOU'VE CONCOCTED, EMILY.

10:03.894 --> 10:05.485
WHAT THE HELL IS WRONG
WITH YOU?

10:05.485 --> 10:07.437
WELL, YOU'VE GIVEN ME
LITTLE REASON

10:07.437 --> 10:09.029
TO HELP YOU,
LET ALONE LIVE.

10:09.029 --> 10:10.150
IT'S NOT ABOUT US.

10:10.150 --> 10:11.862
IT'S ABOUT EVERYONE ELSE
WHO'S GONNA SUFFER

10:11.862 --> 10:13.193
IF WE DON'T GET OUT
OF HERE ALIVE,

10:13.193 --> 10:14.574
INCLUDING MY FATHER.

10:14.574 --> 10:16.867
YOUR WORDS HOLD NO MEANING
FOR ME ANYMORE.

10:16.867 --> 10:19.449
[ SIGHS ]
 IT'S FUNNY, ISN'T IT?

10:19.449 --> 10:21.451
WHO WOULD HAVE THOUGHT

10:21.451 --> 10:23.744
THAT AFTER
ALL WAS SAID AND DONE,

10:23.744 --> 10:27.457
YOU AND I
WOULD DIE TOGETHER?

10:27.457 --> 10:30.090
[ UP-TEMPO PIANO MUSIC PLAYS ]

10:39.970 --> 10:43.433
KEEPING UP WITH YOUR BROTHER'S
CAMPAIGN, I SEE.

10:43.433 --> 10:47.768
OH, NO.

10:47.768 --> 10:49.980
OH, EASY, DARLING.

10:49.980 --> 10:51.191
OH!

10:51.191 --> 10:52.943
IT'S NOT EVEN NOON,

10:52.943 --> 10:55.155
AND ALREADY YOU'RE TRYING
TO DULL YOUR SENSES.

10:55.155 --> 10:58.368
YOU'RE NOT REALLY HERE.

10:58.368 --> 11:00.781
[ Chuckling ]
WELL, OF COURSE I AM, LOU-LOU.

11:00.781 --> 11:02.542
AREN'T YOU GLAD
TO SEE YOUR MAMA?

11:02.542 --> 11:06.126
YOU MUST BE NOLAN ROSS.

11:06.126 --> 11:08.879
I HAVE HEARD
SO MUCH ABOUT YOU.

11:08.879 --> 11:11.131
PENELOPE ELLIS.

11:11.131 --> 11:13.884
MAMA ELLIS...
IN THE FLESH.

11:13.884 --> 11:15.215
[ CHUCKLES ]
 OH, WOW.

11:15.215 --> 11:16.717
YOU MUST HAVE COME
TO REFILL

11:16.717 --> 11:18.508
YOUR DAUGHTER'S PRESCRIPTIONS,
NO DOUBT?

11:18.508 --> 11:20.510
PARDON?
 OH.

11:20.510 --> 11:22.723
[ CHUCKLES ]
DON'T MIND ME.

11:22.723 --> 11:25.305
LOUISE, DEAR,
GIVE YOUR MAMA A HUG.

11:25.305 --> 11:27.147
[ CHUCKLES ]

11:27.147 --> 11:30.570
OH, I HAVE BEEN WORRIED SICK
ABOUT YOU.

11:32.112 --> 11:34.024
LYMAN SAYS
YOU ARE NOT DOING WELL.

11:34.024 --> 11:36.696
AS YOU CAN SEE,
I'M DOING PERFECTLY FINE.

11:36.696 --> 11:38.779
WHAT WITH HIM BACK OUT
ON THE CAMPAIGN TRAIL,

11:38.779 --> 11:40.991
I THOUGHT MAYBE YOU AND I
COULD SPEND SOME TIME TOGETHER.

11:40.991 --> 11:43.623
OH, WELL, ACTUALLY,
LOUISE AND I HAD PLANS.

11:43.623 --> 11:46.877
A DEEP TISSUE MASSAGE
AND SEAWEED FACIAL AWAITS.

11:46.877 --> 11:48.879
WELL, FINE.

11:48.879 --> 11:50.460
I SHOULD PROBABLY GET BACK
TO THE HOUSE

11:50.460 --> 11:51.752
AND SETTLE IN FIRST.

11:51.752 --> 11:53.213
THE HOUSE?

11:53.213 --> 11:56.216
OH, YOU MEAN YOU'RE
NOT JUST STAYING AT
A HOTEL FOR THE NIGHT?

11:56.216 --> 11:59.139
I HAVE DECIDED TO RENT A PLACE
IN THE HAMPTONS FOR THE SUMMER.

11:59.139 --> 12:03.223
THAT WAY YOU AND I CAN BE CLOSE
TO EACH OTHER ALL THE TIME,

12:03.223 --> 12:06.146
THE WAY
A REAL FAMILY SHOULD BE.

12:08.849 --> 12:11.812
ONE BIG, HAPPY, INDEED.

12:11.812 --> 12:15.275
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

12:18.118 --> 12:19.699
CLARKE.

12:19.699 --> 12:22.122
WELL, YOU WERE ALWAYS
A LITTLE SLOW

12:22.122 --> 12:25.035
WHEN PRESENTED
WITH A TASK, WEREN'T YOU?

12:25.035 --> 12:27.127
I NEEDED TIME
TO GET TO KATE,

12:27.127 --> 12:30.000
BUT I'M HERE NOW
AND LOOKING AT HER.

12:30.000 --> 12:31.541
Kate: YEAH, IT'S ME.

12:31.541 --> 12:33.133
I'M HERE.

12:33.133 --> 12:34.754
KATIE?
KATIE, DARLING?

12:34.754 --> 12:36.216
You can hear her.
She's alive and well.

12:36.216 --> 12:38.088
SO COOPERATE, OR THAT'S
GONNA CHANGE IN A HURRY.

12:38.088 --> 12:40.801
NO, YOU LISTEN TO ME.

12:40.801 --> 12:44.054
This is not
a negotiation.

12:44.054 --> 12:47.307
I WANT
MY DAUGHTER BACK NOW.

12:48.148 --> 12:49.439
IT'S OVER.

12:49.439 --> 12:50.770
I'M SORRY.

12:50.770 --> 12:52.152
JACK.

12:52.152 --> 12:57.777
CLARKE, YOU ARE REALLY,
REALLY TRYING MY PATIENCE.

12:57.777 --> 13:02.402
NOW, LET ME SPEAK
TO MY DAUGHTER.

13:02.402 --> 13:03.783
CEDAR HILL. SUNDOWN.

13:03.783 --> 13:06.166
YOU BRING VICTORIA AND AMANDA,
AND I'LL BRING KATE.

13:06.166 --> 13:07.207
[ BEEP ]

13:17.047 --> 13:18.718
I'M TELLING YOU, WE SHOULD
BRING IN THE S.W.A.T. TEAM.

13:18.718 --> 13:20.010
THEY KNOW HOW TO HANDLE
HOSTAGE SITUATIONS.

13:20.010 --> 13:21.551
MALCOLM ALREADY INFILTRATED
LAW ENFORCEMENT.

13:21.551 --> 13:23.303
KATE WAS PROOF OF THAT,
AS ARE THE FEDS THAT LET HIM GO.

13:23.303 --> 13:24.975
YEAH, BUT ONE OF THOSE HOSTAGES
COULD BE ALVAREZ.

13:24.975 --> 13:26.386
HE WOULD KNOW HOW TO WORK IT
FROM THE INSIDE.

13:26.386 --> 13:28.348
YOU HAVE TO TRUST ME.
 BECAUSE YOU HAVE SUCH
A GREAT TRACK RECORD

13:28.348 --> 13:29.809
WHEN IT COMES TO TRUST?

13:29.809 --> 13:31.731
HEY, I DIDN'T ASK
FOR YOUR HELP.
 GUYS, ENOUGH!

13:31.731 --> 13:33.143
WE ONLY HAVE A FEW HOURS
TILL SUNDOWN.

13:33.143 --> 13:34.855
YOU'RE WASTING
WHAT LITTLE TIME WE HAVE.

13:34.855 --> 13:36.106
THAT EXCHANGE
WITH MALCOLM

13:36.106 --> 13:37.277
IS GONNA HAVE TO BE
OUR LAST RESORT.

13:39.359 --> 13:41.571
FINDING THE WOMEN --
IT'S GONNA BE NEARLY IMPOSSIBLE.

13:41.571 --> 13:43.283
WE COULD CHECK
AT THE STATION --

13:43.283 --> 13:45.575
SEE IF EMILY'S CAR POPPED UP
ON THE ABANDONED-VEHICLE LOG.

13:45.575 --> 13:48.288
IT'S A GOOD PLACE
TO START.

13:48.288 --> 13:50.040
WE'LL FIND THEM, DAVID.

13:50.040 --> 13:51.501
I HOPE YOU'RE RIGHT.

13:57.667 --> 13:59.459
OH.
 [ GASPS ] MOTHER.

13:59.459 --> 14:01.091
OH, YOU'RE NOT LEAVING,
ARE YOU?

14:01.091 --> 14:02.672
I WAS HOPING WE COULD GET
A LATE LUNCH.

14:02.672 --> 14:04.554
I'M AFRAID I'M BUSY.
I'M RUNNING BEHIND --

14:04.554 --> 14:06.806
OH, THIS IS JUST
A LOVELY HOTEL.

14:06.806 --> 14:10.180
AND YOU CERTAINLY ARE
SETTLING IN NICELY AROUND HERE.

14:10.180 --> 14:13.143
I'M SO GLAD
TO SEE YOU HAPPY, LOUISE.

14:13.143 --> 14:14.274
YOU CAN DROP THE ACT NOW,
MOTHER.

14:14.274 --> 14:15.475
WE'RE ALONE.

14:15.475 --> 14:17.107
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

14:17.107 --> 14:20.901
LYMAN SAID YOU GAVE HIM
A LOT OF TROUBLE.

14:20.901 --> 14:23.073
THAT WASN'T VERY NICE.

14:23.073 --> 14:25.365
WELL, NEITHER WAS DRUGGING ME
FOR MOST OF MY LIFE,

14:25.365 --> 14:27.577
BUT THAT DIDN'T SEEM
TO STOP THE TWO OF YOU.

14:27.577 --> 14:29.489
YOU ARE NOT WELL, LOUISE.

14:29.489 --> 14:32.122
YOU HAVEN'T BEEN
EVER SINCE YOUR DADDY DIED.

14:32.122 --> 14:33.994
YOU NEED THOSE PILLS
TO STAY SANE.

14:33.994 --> 14:36.376
THOSE PILLS YOU TRICKED ME
INTO TAKING

14:36.376 --> 14:38.959
HAD HORRIBLE SIDE EFFECTS,
WHICH INCLUDED

14:38.959 --> 14:40.921
SEEING A LOT MORE OF YOU
THAN I WANTED TO.

14:40.921 --> 14:42.302
YES, LYMAN TOLD ME
ABOUT THAT.

14:42.302 --> 14:44.804
YOU SEE, THOSE ARE
EXACTLY THE KIND OF RAVINGS

14:44.804 --> 14:46.056
THAT LED JUDGE MILLER

14:46.056 --> 14:48.768
TO APPOINT ME
YOUR LEGAL CONSERVATOR.

14:48.768 --> 14:52.352
FIRST, YOU START OFF
WITH THAT NASTY ARTICLE,

14:52.352 --> 14:56.356
NOW THESE WILD CLAIMS
ABOUT DRUGGING YOU.

14:56.356 --> 14:59.189
I CAN SEE
I GOT HERE JUST IN TIME.

14:59.189 --> 15:01.361
MY LYMAN HAS POTENTIAL.

15:01.361 --> 15:03.783
I'M GONNA BE THE MOTHER
OF A CONGRESSMAN,

15:03.783 --> 15:05.695
AND I WILL NOT LET YOU
RUIN THAT.

15:08.158 --> 15:10.530
HE ALWAYS DID COME FIRST,
DIDN'T HE?

15:14.084 --> 15:17.207
I'VE ALWAYS LET YOU SPEND
WHATEVER YOU WANTED

15:17.207 --> 15:19.169
AS LONG AS YOU BEHAVED.

15:19.169 --> 15:23.213
NOW, YOU WILL KEEP QUIET,
OR THE MONEY STOPS.

15:23.213 --> 15:26.596
YOU CAN'T CUT ME OFF.

15:26.596 --> 15:28.178
MM.

15:28.178 --> 15:30.350
BUT I CAN.

15:30.350 --> 15:33.183
JUDGE SAID SO.

15:38.358 --> 15:41.111
DON'T FIGHT ME ON THIS,
LOUISE.

15:41.111 --> 15:43.193
YOU'LL COME OUT
ON THE LOSING END,

15:43.193 --> 15:45.615
LIKE ALWAYS.

15:49.949 --> 15:53.573
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

15:58.668 --> 16:00.340
Jack:
THAT'S EMILY'S CAR.

16:02.042 --> 16:03.843
YOU THINK THIS IS WHERE
HE KIDNAPPED HER?

16:03.843 --> 16:05.845
I DON'T KNOW.
 WHAT THE HELL
WAS SHE DOING OUT HERE?

16:05.845 --> 16:07.007
I DON'T KNOW.

16:07.007 --> 16:09.089
I THOUGHT YOU KNEW
EVERYTHING ABOUT HER.

16:09.089 --> 16:12.512
LOOK, I WAS IN THE DARK
FOR A WHILE TOO.

16:12.512 --> 16:14.854
WHEN DID YOU
FIND OUT THE TRUTH?

16:14.854 --> 16:16.096
ABOUT
A YEAR AND A HALF AGO.

16:16.096 --> 16:18.768
WHOA, WHAT, WAIT --
HOW DID THAT FEEL?

16:18.768 --> 16:20.480
KNOWING SHE WAS LYING TO YOU
ABOUT WHO SHE WAS?

16:20.480 --> 16:23.603
IT TOOK ME A WHILE TO MAKE
MY PEACE WITH IT, BUT I DID.

16:23.603 --> 16:25.655
AND I KEPT HER SECRET
BECAUSE --

16:25.655 --> 16:28.068
BECAUSE REVEALING IT
WOULD HAVE HURT HER.

16:28.068 --> 16:29.949
SHE'S ON THE RIGHT SIDE
OF THIS WAR,

16:29.949 --> 16:31.111
WHETHER YOU KNOW IT OR NOT.

16:34.414 --> 16:36.416
[ CAR ALARM BEEPS ]

16:40.830 --> 16:42.122
[ SIGHS ]

16:42.122 --> 16:43.173
[ CAR DOOR SLAMS ]

16:43.173 --> 16:44.504
THERE'S NO SIGN
OF STRUGGLE.

16:44.504 --> 16:46.886
WE DO HAVE A SECURITY CAM,
WHICH MEANS WE CAN SEE

16:46.886 --> 16:48.798
WHAT KIND OF CAR MALCOLM
WAS DRIVING,

16:48.798 --> 16:50.890
MAYBE WHICH WAY
THEY HEADED.

16:50.890 --> 16:54.054
THE PARKS DEPARTMENT
IS NEAR MY HOUSE.

16:54.054 --> 16:56.096
GET THE SECURITY FOOTAGE.
MEET ME THERE AT MY PLACE.

16:56.096 --> 16:57.227
WAIT --
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

16:57.227 --> 16:59.139
TO TELL DAVID
THERE MIGHT BE ANOTHER WAY!

17:01.561 --> 17:05.944
LADIES...
I BROUGHT YOU SOME FOOD.

17:05.944 --> 17:09.529
THOUGHT YOU MIGHT NEED
TO KEEP YOUR STRENGTH UP.

17:09.529 --> 17:13.953
I'D HATE FOR DAVID
TO THINK I WAS MISTREATING YOU.

17:20.039 --> 17:22.212
WHAT'S THE POINT?

17:22.212 --> 17:24.624
YOU'RE GONNA KILL US ANYWAY,
AREN'T YOU?

17:24.624 --> 17:25.835
WHY WAIT FOR DAVID

17:25.835 --> 17:27.467
WHEN THERE'S SOMEONE ELSE
WHO KNOWS WHERE SHE IS?

17:29.929 --> 17:32.222
I'M LISTENING.
 YOU'RE A BUSINESSMAN.

17:32.222 --> 17:35.975
SURELY YOU KNOW THAT
VALUABLE INFORMATION HAS A COST.

17:41.141 --> 17:43.813
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

17:43.813 --> 17:46.186
MY FREEDOM, OF COURSE.

17:46.186 --> 17:48.278
YOU DON'T CAGE
A MAJESTIC PEACOCK

17:48.278 --> 17:49.609
WITH A HOWLER MONKEY.

17:49.609 --> 17:53.113
I'LL GIVE YOU YOUR FREEDOM,

17:53.113 --> 17:57.117
IF YOUR INFORMATION
HAS PROVEN VALUABLE.

17:57.117 --> 17:58.998
VICTORIA,
DON'T SAY ANOTHER WORD.

17:58.998 --> 18:01.291
PERHAPS YOU'VE HEARD
OF A MAN NAMED JACK PORTER?

18:01.291 --> 18:02.832
YEAH.

18:02.832 --> 18:06.256
YOU CAN BE CERTAIN THAT DAVID
MADE JACK AWARE OF HIS PLAN,

18:06.256 --> 18:08.208
SO I WOULD GO FIND HIM
IF I WERE YOU.

18:08.208 --> 18:09.008
HE MIGHT PROVE VERY HELPFUL

18:09.008 --> 18:10.840
AS TO YOUR DAUGHTER'S
WHEREABOUTS.

18:10.840 --> 18:12.762
THIS IS JUST A DESPERATE ATTEMPT
TO SAVE HERSELF

18:12.762 --> 18:14.304
WITH INFORMATION
THAT SHE DOESN'T HAVE.

18:14.304 --> 18:16.306
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]

18:16.306 --> 18:17.927
IVAN.

18:17.927 --> 18:20.140
DON'T YOU DARE.

18:20.140 --> 18:24.103
GO SEE OUR FRIEND
MR. PORTER AGAIN.

18:24.103 --> 18:26.726
FIND OUT WHAT HE KNOWS.

18:27.777 --> 18:29.189
NO!

18:37.447 --> 18:39.449
ENOUGH.

18:39.449 --> 18:42.242
YOU, TIE THEM UP.

18:42.242 --> 18:46.166
THEY JUST WON'T RESPECT
WHAT LITTLE FREEDOM I GIVE THEM.

18:46.166 --> 18:49.169
[ GRUNTING ]

18:49.169 --> 18:52.382
YOU, GET ON YOUR WAY.

18:52.382 --> 18:55.054
AND WHATEVER ANSWERS
YOU GET FROM PORTER,

18:55.054 --> 18:58.638
AFTER THAT,
FEEL FREE TO KILL HIM.

19:10.650 --> 19:12.192
WE FOUND EMILY'S CAR
NEAR THE LIGHTHOUSE.

19:12.192 --> 19:12.982
BEN'S CHECKING
THE SECURITY FOOTAGE

19:12.982 --> 19:14.534
TO SEE
WHAT MALCOLM WAS DRIVING.

19:14.534 --> 19:17.197
WE CAN PUT OUT AN APB
ON HIS CAR.
 IT'S TOO LATE, JACK.

19:17.197 --> 19:18.538
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

19:18.538 --> 19:20.580
THERE'S STILL TIME.
 IT'S ALMOST SUNDOWN.

19:20.580 --> 19:22.161
OKAY.

19:22.161 --> 19:24.083
THEN HOW
ARE WE DOING THIS?

19:24.083 --> 19:27.086
NO, IT'S MY PROBLEM,
NOT YOURS.

19:27.086 --> 19:29.499
YOU CAN'T DO THIS ALONE.

19:29.499 --> 19:31.090
NO, I'M THE ONE TO BLAME.

19:31.090 --> 19:33.253
I PUT MY FRIENDS AND FAMILY
IN HARM'S WAY,

19:33.253 --> 19:34.504
ESPECIALLY AMANDA.

19:34.504 --> 19:35.965
AS SOON AS I FOUND OUT
WHO SHE WAS,

19:35.965 --> 19:37.507
I SHOULD HAVE TAKEN HER AWAY
FROM ALL THIS.

19:37.507 --> 19:39.929
NOW I MIGHT LOSE HER

19:39.929 --> 19:42.181
WITHOUT EVEN SPENDING A DAY
WITH HER.

19:42.181 --> 19:44.224
I'VE SEEN HER THROUGH A LOT
IN THESE LAST FEW YEARS,

19:44.224 --> 19:45.395
AND IF THERE'S ONE THING
I KNOW

19:45.395 --> 19:47.146
IT'S THAT SHE CAN TAKE CARE
OF HERSELF.

19:48.728 --> 19:50.520
SHE'LL FIND A WAY
TO SURVIVE, DAVID.

19:50.520 --> 19:51.611
SHE ALWAYS HAS.

19:51.611 --> 19:53.523
IN A FEW HOURS,
THIS WILL ALL BE OVER --

19:53.523 --> 19:54.774
ONE WAY OR THE OTHER.

19:54.774 --> 19:57.156
WELL, I'M NOT GIVING UP.

20:04.284 --> 20:06.035
YOU KNOW,

20:06.035 --> 20:07.997
WHEN YOU WALKED UP TO ME
AT THE LIGHTHOUSE,

20:07.997 --> 20:10.089
I THOUGHT
YOU WERE GOING TO KILL ME.

20:10.089 --> 20:12.752
NOW I WISHED YOU HAD.

20:12.752 --> 20:14.504
YOU AND I BOTH KNOW

20:14.504 --> 20:16.336
THAT WE'RE ONLY
IN THIS SITUATION

20:16.336 --> 20:18.217
BECAUSE OF THE PHOTO
THAT YOU SENT

20:18.217 --> 20:20.099
THAT LED KATE STRAIGHT
TO ME.

20:20.099 --> 20:22.101
YOU WERE ALREADY ONTO KATE,

20:22.101 --> 20:24.053
AND WE WERE BOTH
JUST TRYING TO HELP DAVID.

20:24.053 --> 20:26.266
IT ALL COMES BACK TO MY FATHER,
DOESN'T IT?

20:26.266 --> 20:29.108
ARE YOU DRIVEN
BY THE GUILT YOU HAVE

20:29.108 --> 20:30.730
FOR WHAT YOU DID TO HIM?

20:30.730 --> 20:31.901
LOVE IS COMPLICATED.

20:31.901 --> 20:33.062
HE DOESN'T LOVE YOU.

20:35.315 --> 20:37.817
HOW DO YOU THINK I KNEW
TO SEND YOU TO THE LIGHTHOUSE?

20:39.859 --> 20:43.122
MY FATHER SAID THAT IT WOULD BE
THE PERFECT PLACE

20:43.122 --> 20:46.666
TO STAGE
A GRIEVING MOTHER'S SUICIDE.

20:48.077 --> 20:51.501
FROM THE MOMENT MY FATHER
RETURNED TO THE HAMPTONS,

20:51.501 --> 20:54.464
HE'S BEEN PLOTTING
YOUR DEATH.

20:56.926 --> 20:59.088
Malcolm: LADIES.

20:59.088 --> 21:02.382
NICE TO SEE YOU TWO
FINALLY SETTLING IN,

21:02.382 --> 21:06.936
BUT I'M AFRAID IT'S TIME
TO TAKE A LITTLE FIELD TRIP.

21:10.059 --> 21:14.394
SO, LET ME GET THIS STRAIGHT --
YOU BREATHE A WORD TO ANYONE

21:14.394 --> 21:17.817
ABOUT THE DOSING
AND SHE CUTS YOU OFF?

21:17.817 --> 21:19.399
SOUNDS ABOUT RIGHT.

21:19.399 --> 21:20.900
[ SIGHS ]

21:20.900 --> 21:23.363
YOUR FATHER LEFT YOU
 THAT MONEY.

21:23.363 --> 21:27.166
YOU'RE OFF THE PILLS, ERGO,
NO LONGER CRAY-CRAY.

21:27.166 --> 21:29.409
YOU CAN MAKE DECISIONS
FOR YOURSELF.

21:29.409 --> 21:32.752
YEAH, TRY TELLING THAT
TO ANY JUDGE IN SAVANNAH.

21:32.752 --> 21:34.213
MY MOM'S GOT A TEAM
OF LAWYERS

21:34.213 --> 21:36.005
THAT HAS EVERY ONE
OF THEM PAID OFF,

21:36.005 --> 21:38.878
WHICH MEANS
THE CONSERVATORSHIP STICKS

21:38.878 --> 21:40.800
AND SHE KEEPS CONTROL
OF MY MONEY.

21:40.800 --> 21:43.092
HOW DID YOU PUT UP
WITH HER ALL THOSE YEARS?

21:43.092 --> 21:44.884
OH, EASY.

21:44.884 --> 21:47.136
I HAD MY DADDY.

21:47.136 --> 21:48.928
[ CHUCKLES ]
 I REMEMBER THIS ONE TIME,

21:48.928 --> 21:51.230
SHE TRIED TO BANISH ME
TO BOARDING SCHOOL,

21:51.230 --> 21:52.812
BUT WHEN WE GOT THERE,

21:52.812 --> 21:55.194
MY FATHER WAS WAITING
ON THE STEPS.

21:55.194 --> 21:57.066
HE PUT ME BACK IN THE CAR
AND TOLD HER

21:57.066 --> 21:59.108
SHE COULD FIND
HER OWN WAY HOME.
 [ LAUGHS ]

21:59.108 --> 22:01.320
IT SOUNDS LIKE
HE WAS THE ONLY ONE

22:01.320 --> 22:04.283
WHO WAS ABLE TO GO A FEW ROUNDS
WITH MOMMY DEAREST.

22:04.283 --> 22:08.287
YEAH, HE JUST COULDN'T WIN
THE FIGHT WITH HIMSELF.

22:08.287 --> 22:10.910
HE KNEW HIS DRINKING
WOULD GET THE BEST OF HIM,

22:10.910 --> 22:13.913
WHICH IS I THINK
HE LEFT ME THE MONEY.

22:13.913 --> 22:16.045
HE WANTED ME TO BE SAFE
FROM HER.

22:16.045 --> 22:18.918
AND YET,
THAT IS EXACTLY THE THING

22:18.918 --> 22:21.511
THAT'S PUTTING YOU
IN DANGER RIGHT NOW.

22:21.511 --> 22:24.514
[ SIGHS ]
I'M SCARED, NOLAN.

22:26.966 --> 22:29.138
WITHOUT MY BANK ACCOUNT,
I JUST --

22:29.138 --> 22:31.521
I DON'T KNOW HOW TO LIVE.
 [ CHUCKLES ]

22:31.521 --> 22:34.894
MAMA DESERVES TO SUFFER
FOR WHAT SHE DID,

22:34.894 --> 22:37.316
BUT I DON'T THINK
I CAN MAKE IT ON MY OWN.

22:37.316 --> 22:38.978
AND YOU CAN'T GIVE UP.

22:38.978 --> 22:42.191
YOUR DADDY WANTED YOU
TO HAVE THAT MONEY, NOT HER.

22:42.191 --> 22:45.194
THERE'S GOT TO BE
ANOTHER WAY.

22:45.194 --> 22:48.037
WE JUST...

22:48.037 --> 22:51.040
WE HAVEN'T
FIGURED IT OUT YET.

22:52.492 --> 22:55.495
YOU FIND ANYTHING
ON THE TAPES?

22:57.086 --> 22:58.708
BEN?

22:58.708 --> 23:01.090
[ MUFFLED SHOUTING ]
 WHAT THE HELL?

23:06.175 --> 23:08.267
[ BOTH GRUNTING, GROANING ]

23:29.288 --> 23:31.871
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

23:53.973 --> 23:57.106
BEEN A LONG TIME, CLARKE.

23:57.106 --> 23:58.728
YEAH, NOT LONG ENOUGH.

23:58.728 --> 24:00.189
WHERE'S MY DAUGHTER?

24:13.372 --> 24:14.954
WHERE'S AMANDA?

24:16.746 --> 24:19.168
YOU DIDN'T THINK
I'D BRING BOTH OF THEM

24:19.168 --> 24:22.081
UNTIL I KNOW
THAT MY DAUGHTER IS SAFE?

24:22.081 --> 24:24.173
KATE'S IN THE VAN,
BUT I EXPECT TO SEE AMANDA --

24:24.173 --> 24:26.385
SHUT UP.

24:32.221 --> 24:34.353
[ BEEPING ]

24:36.726 --> 24:37.937
DON'T BOTHER.

24:39.058 --> 24:42.481
HOW STUPID
DO YOU THINK I AM?

24:42.481 --> 24:45.064
SHE WAS NEVER ALIVE,

24:45.064 --> 24:47.697
AND YOU'RE GONNA SUFFER
THE SAME FATE.

24:49.779 --> 24:51.070
OH!
 Victoria: NO!

24:51.070 --> 24:52.161
OH!

24:56.205 --> 24:57.787
GO AHEAD.
GET IT OVER WITH.

25:00.119 --> 25:01.541
YOU KNOW WHAT?

25:01.541 --> 25:04.173
THAT WOULD BE TOO EASY,
MY FRIEND.

25:04.173 --> 25:09.589
I'M GONNA NEED
TO SEE YOU SUFFER FIRST.

25:16.135 --> 25:17.847
THIS GUY
GOT THE JUMP ON ME

25:17.847 --> 25:20.099
WHILE I WAS WATCHING
THE SECURITY FOOTAGE.

25:20.099 --> 25:21.020
HE THOUGHT I WAS YOU,

25:21.020 --> 25:23.232
WANTED TO KNOW
WHERE KATE WAS BEING HELD.

25:23.232 --> 25:25.194
HOW DID MALCOLM FIGURE OUT
I WAS INVOLVED?

25:25.194 --> 25:28.197
HELL IF I KNOW.

25:28.197 --> 25:30.650
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]
WHAT DID YOU FIND ON THE TAPES?

25:30.650 --> 25:32.151
NOTHING.

25:32.151 --> 25:34.914
EMILY'S CAR WAS THE LAST
TO PULL INTO THE LOT.

25:34.914 --> 25:36.916
NOBODY CAME IN
OR LEFT AFTER HER.

25:36.916 --> 25:38.868
IT DOESN'T MAKE ANY SENSE.

25:38.868 --> 25:40.620
EVEN WHEN
THIS GUY WAKES UP,

25:40.620 --> 25:43.002
HE'S NEVER GIVE UP
MALCOLM'S LOCATION.

25:43.002 --> 25:45.004
[ SIGHS ]

25:46.796 --> 25:49.168
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

25:49.168 --> 25:52.511
THIS -- THIS --
IT'S A MESSAGE FROM EMILY.

25:52.511 --> 25:53.933
A STAR?

25:53.933 --> 25:55.725
NO, WHEN WE WERE KIDS,

25:55.725 --> 25:57.096
WE -- WE WOULD PLAY
TREASURE HUNT,

25:57.096 --> 25:58.227
AND W-WE'D DRAW A MAP,

25:58.227 --> 25:59.348
AND WE'D PUT A STAR
WITH A CIRCLE ON IT --

25:59.348 --> 26:01.270
THAT'S WHERE
THE TREASURE WAS BURIED.

26:01.270 --> 26:02.942
I KNOW IT SOUNDS CRAZY.
 WHAT?

26:02.942 --> 26:04.563
OKAY, BUT, I MEAN,
WITHOUT A MAP,

26:04.563 --> 26:06.315
YOU DON'T REALLY HAVE MUCH
TO GO ON.

26:06.315 --> 26:09.528
WE GOT TO BE
MISSING SOMETHING.

26:09.528 --> 26:11.240
[ SIGHS ]

26:11.240 --> 26:14.033
I'M NOT SURE IT MATTERS.

26:14.033 --> 26:16.996
IT'S DARK NOW.
WE NEVER HEARD BACK FROM DAVID.

26:16.996 --> 26:19.038
MAYBE WE'RE TOO LATE.

26:27.757 --> 26:29.128
[ SNIFFS ]

26:29.128 --> 26:31.210
THIS GUY'S BEEN WALKING
THROUGH COAL.

26:36.636 --> 26:38.347
SHE USED THIS
TO DRAW THAT.

26:38.347 --> 26:42.141
NO OTHER CARS PULLED
INTO THE LOT LAST NIGHT

26:42.141 --> 26:44.183
BECAUSE SHE WASN'T TAKEN
BY CAR.

26:44.183 --> 26:46.395
SHE WAS TAKEN BY BOAT
TO THE ONE PLACE

26:46.395 --> 26:49.068
THAT STILL USES COAL
FOR THEIR INCINERATOR.

26:49.068 --> 26:50.780
THE TRASH YARD
DOWN ON THE WATER.

26:58.948 --> 27:00.079
WHAT HAPPENED?

27:00.079 --> 27:02.081
IT'S OVER.

27:07.006 --> 27:08.798
[ GROANS ]

27:08.798 --> 27:11.210
SIT DOWN.

27:13.713 --> 27:16.095
LET THEM GO.

27:16.095 --> 27:18.888
ALL THE TIME
WE'VE BEEN TOGETHER,

27:18.888 --> 27:22.181
YOU SHOULD KNOW ME
BETTER THAN THAT.

27:24.684 --> 27:26.565
I'M GONNA KILL YOU.

27:26.565 --> 27:28.477
THAT'S FOR DAMN SURE.

27:28.477 --> 27:32.191
BUT I THOUGHT IT'D BE BE
MORE FUN FOR YOU

27:32.191 --> 27:33.823
TO WATCH THEM DIE FIRST.

27:33.823 --> 27:37.036
THEY GOT NOTHING TO DO WITH IT.
IT'S ME YOU WANT.

27:40.619 --> 27:43.122
[ SCREAMS ]

27:43.122 --> 27:45.624
[ GROANING ]

27:51.050 --> 27:53.052
YOU KNOW WHAT?

27:53.052 --> 27:55.214
YOU'RE RIGHT.

27:55.214 --> 27:58.217
BUT JUST
FOR OLD TIME'S SAKE,

27:58.217 --> 28:02.852
WHY DON'T YOU DO THE WORK
WHILE I WATCH?

28:11.901 --> 28:15.154
I KNOW IN THE PAST YOU WERE
OF GREAT HELP TO MY FATHER

28:15.154 --> 28:18.697
WHEN HE NEEDED THINGS
TAKEN CARE OF.

28:18.697 --> 28:21.160
PASCAL
WAS VERY GOOD TO ME.

28:21.160 --> 28:24.163
MAY HE REST IN PEACE.

28:24.163 --> 28:28.207
AND THAT APPRECIATION
WILL CONTINUE.

28:28.207 --> 28:32.041
THERE'S A WOMAN WHO NEEDS
TO PAY FOR CROSSING ME.

28:32.041 --> 28:34.383
YOU WANT ME TO PIN SOMETHING
ON HER?

28:34.383 --> 28:36.545
THAT WON'T BE NECESSARY.

28:36.545 --> 28:39.298
SHE'S ALREADY COMMITTED
THE CRIMES.

28:42.892 --> 28:45.144
THEN WHY NOT TURN HER OVER
TO THE POLICE?

28:45.144 --> 28:48.147
I'M MISSING
ONE CRUCIAL DETAIL --

28:48.147 --> 28:50.940
EVIDENCE.

28:50.940 --> 28:52.351
THAT'S WHERE YOU COME IN.

28:52.351 --> 28:54.193
I'LL START
BY TAPPING HER PHONE.

28:54.193 --> 28:56.355
ALL I NEED'S A NAME
AND A NUMBER.

28:56.355 --> 28:58.697
I GET QUICK RESULTS.

28:58.697 --> 29:03.122
QUICK RESULTS ARE
EXACTLY WHAT I'M LOOKING FOR.

29:06.125 --> 29:08.958
Malcolm:
I'M WAITING, CLARKE.

29:12.631 --> 29:15.044
I SAID...

29:15.044 --> 29:16.675
I'M WAITING, CLARKE!
 [ SCREAMS ]

29:16.675 --> 29:17.877
LEAVE HIM ALONE!

29:17.877 --> 29:20.429
GO TO HELL!

29:20.429 --> 29:22.842
GO TO HELL?

29:28.687 --> 29:31.060
GREAT IDEA!

29:36.856 --> 29:38.487
HOW'S THAT FOR HELL?!

29:38.487 --> 29:42.031
YOU HAD TO MAKE IT COMPLICATED.

29:42.031 --> 29:44.573
ONE SLIT ACROSS THE THROAT,

29:44.573 --> 29:47.706
AND IT'D HAVE BEEN A QUICK DEATH
FOR BOTH OF THEM.

29:47.706 --> 29:52.621
SO, NOW WE DO IT MY WAY...

29:54.834 --> 29:56.585
...IN PIECES.

29:57.837 --> 29:59.839
IT'S EASIER
TO BURN THE EVIDENCE.

30:04.383 --> 30:06.225
NO, WAIT.

30:06.225 --> 30:07.016
WAIT.

30:07.016 --> 30:08.637
HEY!

30:08.637 --> 30:11.230
STAY AWAY FROM HER!

30:12.101 --> 30:15.194
[ GROANS ]

30:15.194 --> 30:19.818
THIS IS
FOR KILLING MY DAUGHTER.

30:19.818 --> 30:20.990
Victoria: I DID IT!

30:20.990 --> 30:24.033
I KILLED KATE.

30:24.033 --> 30:26.075
SHE MURDERED MY SON,

30:26.075 --> 30:29.118
AND I SHOT THAT BITCH
IN COLD BLOOD.

30:29.118 --> 30:30.749
YOU?

30:32.872 --> 30:35.084
YOU!

30:35.084 --> 30:36.375
YOU KNOW THE BEST PART?

30:37.456 --> 30:39.418
I LOVED IT.

30:40.669 --> 30:42.301
[ SPITS ]

30:45.424 --> 30:46.765
[ GASPS ]

30:50.139 --> 30:52.932
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

30:52.932 --> 30:53.973
GO AHEAD.

30:53.973 --> 30:56.025
STAB ME LIKE A COWARD.

30:56.025 --> 30:57.566
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

30:57.566 --> 31:00.439
LIKE A COWARD?

31:00.439 --> 31:02.861
[ GROANS ]

31:02.861 --> 31:04.984
[ WHIMPERS ]

31:08.657 --> 31:11.580
[ GASPING ]

31:11.580 --> 31:13.042
Jack: LET HER GO!

31:14.123 --> 31:16.255
NOT ANOTHER MOVE.

31:16.255 --> 31:19.128
[ GASPING ]

31:21.340 --> 31:24.093
[ GRUNTING, GROANING ]

31:31.060 --> 31:33.892
[ GRUNTS ]

31:39.778 --> 31:41.570
[ GUNSHOT ]

32:05.044 --> 32:07.806
WE'RE GONNA GET YOU
OUT OF HERE.
 NO.

32:07.806 --> 32:09.808
EMILY!

32:14.393 --> 32:15.314
WAIT.

32:26.405 --> 32:27.326
NO!

32:27.326 --> 32:29.068
[ GUNSHOTS ]

32:34.333 --> 32:37.076
[ GUNSHOTS ]

32:58.187 --> 33:00.979
DRAWING OUR TREASURE-HUNT SIGN
ON MALCOLM'S GUNMAN

33:00.979 --> 33:02.401
WAS A SMART MOVE.

33:02.401 --> 33:06.025
AFTER I CONVINCED VICTORIA
TO CREATE A DISTRACTION.

33:06.025 --> 33:09.948
I GUESS HER GUILT IS
FINALLY CATCHING UP WITH HER.

33:09.948 --> 33:12.871
SHE KNEW SHE HAD TO HELP.

33:12.871 --> 33:14.243
I'M GLAD SHE DID.

33:14.243 --> 33:16.245
IT MADE ALL THE DIFFERENCE.

33:16.245 --> 33:17.576
YOU'RE STILL HERE.

33:19.458 --> 33:21.040
[ SIGHS ]

33:21.040 --> 33:23.882
I WAS OUT OF OPTIONS.

33:23.882 --> 33:25.884
BUT I KNEW
THAT YOU AND MY FATHER

33:25.884 --> 33:27.796
WERE WORKING TOGETHER

33:27.796 --> 33:30.469
AND THAT YOU'D BE
ALL RIGHT.

33:30.469 --> 33:34.223
WELL, WE HAD A LITTLE HELP
FROM BEN, TOO.

33:34.223 --> 33:36.805
THEY FOUND ALVAREZ'S
PERSONAL EFFECTS

33:36.805 --> 33:38.847
AT THE WAREHOUSE.

33:38.847 --> 33:41.270
HE'S TAKING IT
PRETTY HARD.

33:41.270 --> 33:44.943
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA TELL
THE DETECTIVES?

33:44.943 --> 33:46.695
I'LL START
WITH THE TRUTH --

33:46.695 --> 33:49.528
THAT MALCOLM WAS RELEASED
BY DOUBLE AGENTS WITHIN THE FBI

33:49.528 --> 33:51.570
AND WE DIDN'T KNOW
WHO WE COULD TRUST.

33:53.782 --> 33:56.205
I'M NOT SURE IT'LL BE
THAT EASY

33:56.205 --> 33:57.826
TO EXPLAIN ALL OF THIS
TO BEN.

33:57.826 --> 34:01.120
IT'LL BE EASIER
THAN YOU THINK.

34:03.422 --> 34:05.424
[ SIRENS WAIL IN DISTANCE ]

34:05.424 --> 34:08.005
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

34:08.005 --> 34:09.838
DAVID.

34:09.838 --> 34:11.170
HEY.

34:11.170 --> 34:14.092
I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU DID THAT --

34:14.092 --> 34:17.976
TAKING THE BLAME
FOR KILLING KATE

34:17.976 --> 34:19.638
AND SAVING AMANDA.

34:19.638 --> 34:21.600
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
TO SAY.

34:21.600 --> 34:23.482
EMILY AND I UNITED
IN A PLAN

34:23.482 --> 34:26.105
THAT WE HOPED WOULD LEAD JACK
TO FIND US.

34:26.105 --> 34:31.069
I THOUGHT I'D SACRIFICE MYSELF
TO BUY YOU BOTH MORE TIME.

34:31.069 --> 34:32.991
IT WORKED.

34:32.991 --> 34:36.114
I NOW KNOW THAT YOU WERE
TRYING TO KILL ME,

34:36.114 --> 34:39.788
BEFORE I CONFESSED MY SINS
TO YOU AND EVEN AFTER.

34:39.788 --> 34:41.370
[ SIGHS ]

34:41.370 --> 34:43.161
VICTORIA...

34:43.161 --> 34:45.043
YOU KNOW,
I COULD CALL THE POLICE

34:45.043 --> 34:47.166
AND REVEAL YOUR SINS TO THEM,
BUT I WON'T.

34:50.969 --> 34:54.052
YOU AND EMILY
DESERVE A LIFE TOGETHER.

34:57.766 --> 34:59.638
I NEED TO MOURN MY SON.

34:59.638 --> 35:02.221
IT'S WHAT
WE ALL DESERVE.

35:02.221 --> 35:04.563
WE NEED TO GO
OUR SEPARATE WAYS, DAVID.

35:06.104 --> 35:08.227
GOODBYE.

35:25.123 --> 35:27.125
[ MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS ]

35:30.709 --> 35:33.302
[ LAUGHS ]

35:33.302 --> 35:34.593
WHOO.

35:38.927 --> 35:41.099
I GOT YOUR MESSAGE.
WHAT ARE WE CELEBRATING?

35:41.099 --> 35:44.223
THE END OF YOUR CONTROL
OVER LOUISE.

35:44.223 --> 35:48.146
MY LEGAL TEAM FOUND A LOOPHOLE
IN YOUR CONSERVATORSHIP.

35:48.146 --> 35:50.529
SEEMS YOU ONLY REMAIN
IN CHARGE OF YOUR DAUGHTER...

35:50.529 --> 35:52.191
UNTIL SHE FINDS A HUSBAND.

35:52.191 --> 35:53.572
OH?

35:53.572 --> 35:55.904
GUESS
WHO JUST GOT MARRIED.

35:55.904 --> 35:59.198
YOU DID WHAT?

35:59.198 --> 36:00.579
[ CHUCKLES ]

36:00.579 --> 36:03.452
AND THAT MAKES ME
 HER CONSERVATOR NOW,

36:03.452 --> 36:07.456
WHICH MEANS LOUISE
IS FINALLY FREE OF YOU.

36:09.047 --> 36:10.669
PENNY FOR YOUR THOUGHTS?

36:10.669 --> 36:13.922
I THINK CONGRATULATIONS
ARE IN ORDER.

36:13.922 --> 36:18.096
I THINK I WILL GRAB US A BOTTLE
OF OUR BEST DOM TO CELEBRATE.

36:18.096 --> 36:20.639
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

36:23.011 --> 36:25.183
DO YOU REALLY THINK
YOU'VE WON?

36:25.183 --> 36:26.895
WELL...

36:26.895 --> 36:29.398
THE LAW IS THE LAW,
MOTHER.

36:29.398 --> 36:33.362
MM-HMM. IT WAS A CLEVER ATTEMPT,
DEAR, BUT THIS IS NOT OVER,

36:33.362 --> 36:35.574
AND YOU WILL
GIVE ME CONTROL BACK,

36:35.574 --> 36:37.486
OR THE REAL TRUTH
WILL COME OUT.

36:37.486 --> 36:39.368
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

36:39.368 --> 36:44.783
THOSE PILLS ONLY HELPED
YOUR FEEBLE, LITTLE MIND

36:44.783 --> 36:47.786
TO FORGET
WHAT YOU REALLY DID.

36:49.248 --> 36:51.169
YOU KILLED YOUR FATHER.

36:51.169 --> 36:53.592
AND ONCE I TELL
THAT NEW HUSBAND OF YOURS

36:53.592 --> 36:55.133
AND THE REST OF THE WORLD,

36:55.133 --> 36:58.046
YOU WILL TRULY BE LEFT
WITH NOTHING.

36:58.046 --> 37:01.099
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:01.099 --> 37:03.932
JUST LIKE YOU DESERVE.

37:06.975 --> 37:08.977
[ SCOFFS ]

37:20.989 --> 37:22.951
[ DOOR OPENS ]

37:24.162 --> 37:26.164
Emily: DAD, WHY AREN'T YOU
AT THE HOSPITAL?

37:26.164 --> 37:28.076
I WAS GETTING TREATED

37:28.076 --> 37:30.078
WHEN I HEARD HIM ARGUING
WITH THE DOCTORS.

37:30.078 --> 37:32.080
THEY WANTED HIM
TO STAY THE NIGHT,

37:32.080 --> 37:33.632
BUT HE WASN'T HAVING IT.

37:33.632 --> 37:35.424
[ SIGHS ]
HE'S STUBBORN.

37:35.424 --> 37:38.677
YEAH, WELL,
RUNS IN THE FAMILY.

37:38.677 --> 37:41.970
YEAH, I'M STARTING
TO SEE THAT.

37:41.970 --> 37:44.182
WELL, I TOLD THE DOCS
I'D GET HIM HOME SAFE.

37:44.182 --> 37:46.595
THANK YOU.
WE OWE YOU A LOT.

37:47.766 --> 37:50.309
WELL,
I'LL TAKE IT FROM HERE.

37:55.654 --> 37:58.066
WELL, GOOD NIGHT.

37:58.066 --> 37:59.157
BEN, WAIT.

38:01.029 --> 38:03.742
I DON'T KNOW WHAT WE DID
TO DESERVE YOUR HELP, BUT --

38:03.742 --> 38:06.455
I'M JUST GLAD
YOU'RE BOTH OKAY.

38:06.455 --> 38:08.116
WHY ARE YOU HELPING US?

38:09.708 --> 38:11.039
I SPOKE TO JACK.

38:11.039 --> 38:14.042
I KNOW THAT YOU KNOW.

38:15.964 --> 38:17.546
I'M SORRY.

38:17.546 --> 38:19.628
I WAS RELIEVED,
ACTUALLY.

38:19.628 --> 38:21.630
ALL THIS TIME,
I THOUGHT THE REASON

38:21.630 --> 38:23.261
YOU WERE ALWAYS ACTING
SO WEIRD AROUND ME

38:23.261 --> 38:24.262
WAS BECAUSE OF ME.

38:24.262 --> 38:25.594
[ CHUCKLES ]

38:25.594 --> 38:27.346
NOT TRUE.

38:27.346 --> 38:29.017
AND AS TO WHY I'M HELPING --

38:29.017 --> 38:31.770
WHEN I WAS A ROOKIE,
I WORKED UNDERCOVER.

38:31.770 --> 38:33.311
AND I HAD TO ASSUME
ANOTHER IDENTITY FOR MONTHS

38:33.311 --> 38:35.193
TO HELP TAKE DOWN
A DRUG RING.

38:35.193 --> 38:37.606
SO YOU THINK YOU KNOW
WHAT I WENT THROUGH?
 NO.

38:37.606 --> 38:39.648
NO, NO, THAT'S NOT WHAT
I'M SAYING AT ALL,

38:39.648 --> 38:42.651
BUT -- BUT I DO UNDERSTAND
HOW HARD IT IS

38:42.651 --> 38:44.363
TO BREAK PEOPLE'S TRUST
IN ORDER TO PROTECT THEM.

38:46.034 --> 38:49.998
NOT BEING ABLE TO BE YOURSELF,
HAVING TO PUSH PEOPLE AWAY.

38:49.998 --> 38:52.831
IT GETS TO YOU
AFTER A WHILE.

38:52.831 --> 38:54.833
IT'S LONELY.

38:54.833 --> 38:56.294
[ SIGHS ]

38:56.294 --> 38:58.837
SO, WHILE I DON'T KNOW EXACTLY
WHAT YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH,

38:58.837 --> 39:00.879
I KNOW IT MUST'VE BEEN
FOR THE RIGHT REASONS

39:00.879 --> 39:02.721
IF YOU WERE WILLING
TO SACRIFICE SO MUCH.

39:02.721 --> 39:05.424
THANK YOU
FOR SAYING THAT.

39:05.424 --> 39:08.427
AND YOU DON'T HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT THIS GOING ANY FURTHER.

39:11.229 --> 39:12.811
SO WHAT DO YOU SAY,
BEGINNING TOMORROW,

39:12.811 --> 39:14.973
WE -- WE START OVER?

39:14.973 --> 39:18.937
I'D SAY I'D LIKE THAT
VERY MUCH.

39:18.937 --> 39:20.068
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:21.319 --> 39:23.151
GOOD NIGHT.

39:23.151 --> 39:24.983
GOOD NIGHT.

39:28.747 --> 39:31.329
VICTORIA...

39:31.329 --> 39:34.162
HOW AWFUL.

39:34.162 --> 39:37.996
AND TO KNOW DAVID HAS BEEN
BETRAYING YOU ALL ALONG.

39:37.996 --> 39:40.419
WELL, A PART OF ME SENSED
THAT HIS FEELINGS

39:40.419 --> 39:42.300
WEREN'T GENUINE
FOR SOME TIME.

39:42.300 --> 39:44.382
I'M JUST GLAD I KNOW
FOR CERTAIN.

39:44.382 --> 39:45.964
WELL...

39:45.964 --> 39:50.178
WHICH MEANS YOUR LOYALTY TO HIM
IS NO LONGER WARRANTED.

39:50.178 --> 39:52.681
EMILY DESERVES TO PAY
FOR WHAT SHE'S DONE.

39:52.681 --> 39:55.103
SHE MAY NOT HAVE PUT THE BULLET
IN DANIEL,

39:55.103 --> 39:57.105
BUT SHE'S THE REASON
SO MUCH MISERY

39:57.105 --> 39:58.106
HAS COME INTO OUR LIVES.

39:58.106 --> 40:00.398
AN EXPOSÃ© SPLASHED ACROSS

40:00.398 --> 40:02.110
MY MEDIA OUTLETS
AROUND THE WORLD

40:02.110 --> 40:04.192
COULD LEAD
TO A LENGTHY PRISON SENTENCE.

40:04.192 --> 40:07.486
EMILY'S
NOT WORTH YOUR TIME.

40:09.448 --> 40:13.241
BESIDES,
REVENGE IS A DANGEROUS GAME.

40:13.241 --> 40:16.244
AND THE ONLY THING
THAT'S IMPORTANT TO ME NOW

40:16.244 --> 40:17.996
IS YOU AND MY GRANDCHILD.

40:17.996 --> 40:21.089
AND YOU'RE IMPORTANT TO ME,
AS WELL.

40:22.751 --> 40:28.136
BUT HONORING DANIEL'S MEMORY
IS SOMETHING I HAVE TO DO.

40:34.933 --> 40:37.315
VERY WELL.

40:37.315 --> 40:41.109
BUT HEED MY WARNING --

40:41.109 --> 40:44.773
EMILY HASN'T LEFT A TRAIL
OF EVIDENCE.

40:44.773 --> 40:49.197
DO NOT DO ANYTHING UNTIL
YOU HAVE IRREFUTABLE PROOF.

40:51.329 --> 40:53.121
NOT TO WORRY.

40:53.121 --> 40:57.125
I HAVE A WAY
TO GET THE EVIDENCE I NEED.

40:57.125 --> 41:01.580
IT WILL BE ME
 WHO DESTROYS HER.
